===Noun===
'''domino'''  (''plural'' '''dominos''' or ''dominoes'')

#A [[rectangular]] [[block]] divided into two [[square]]s, each having 0 to 6 [[dot]]s (as in [[dice]]), used in the [[game]] of [[dominoes]].
#(''politics'') A [[country]] that is expected to [[react]] to [[event]]s in a [[neighboring]] country, according to the [[domino effect]]
#A [[masquerade]] [[costume]] consisting of a [[hooded]] [[robe]] and a [[mask]] covering the upper part of the [[face]].
#The mask itself.
#The person wearing the costume.
#{{geometry}} A [[polyomino]] made up of two squares.

